cell("code","def insertion_sort(arr):\n    a = list(arr)\n    for i in range(1, len(a)):\n        # Check a[i] and swap backwards if needed\n        # YOUR CODE HERE\n        pass\n    return a\n\n# print(insertion_sort([3, 5, 8, 2, 5]))"),
cell("markdown","### Step 4: Counting Sort\n1. Find `min` and subtract it from all elements.\n2. Find `max` (of the shifted elements) and create a `counts` array of size `max + 1`.\n3. Count frequencies.\n4. Rebuild the array and add `min` back."),
