cell("markdown","---\n## Phase 1 — Algorithm Construction\n\n### Step 1: Merge Sort\nNow implement the recursive `merge_sort(arr)` function. Use array slicing `arr[:mid]` to split the array."),
cell("code","def merge_sort(arr):\n    '''Return a sorted array using Merge Sort.'''\n    # Base case\n    if len(arr) <= 1: \n        return arr\n    \n    # Divide\n    mid = len(arr) // 2\n    left = arr[:mid]\n    right = arr[mid:]\n    \n    # Conquer (Recursion)\n    # YOUR CODE HERE\n    \n    # Combine\n    # YOUR CODE HERE (use your merge helper)\n    pass\n\n# print(merge_sort([3, 5, 8, 2, 5, 1, 9, 0]))"),
